Wheelo is the all-in-one app for motorcyclists, designed to make motorcycle trips safer, more engaging, and informative. It offers an advanced GPS navigator with alerts for dangerous curves and speed cameras, detailed weather forecasts, smart vehicle maintenance management with reminders, and an SOS button for emergencies. The app includes over 5,000 shared itineraries, group GPS tracking, integrated chat features, and tools to plan motorcycle trips and meetups.

ORGANIZE WITH JUST A FEW CLICKS
Access the "Create Events" section and select the type of event you want to organize (a motorcycle trip or a meetup). Once you’ve defined the route or meeting point, easily invite all participants.

USE THE CHAT
After confirming participation in an event, you’ll gain access to a chat where you can interact with other participants in real time.

CREATE OR CHOOSE THE BEST ROUTE FOR YOU
With Wheelo, you can create customized itineraries and share them with the entire community.

SAFETY
Safety is our top priority: you can report any issues with your motorcycle using the SOS button, which will notify all users within a 50 km radius who may be able to assist you.

WITH WHEELO YOU CAN:

- Connect with other motorcyclists who share your interests;
- Create private events, visible only to your selected friends;
- Organize personalized motorcycle trips and meetups tailored to your preferences;
- Quickly and easily participate in events and meetups;
- Create detailed itineraries, specifying route characteristics, and share them;
- Start single or group tracking to monitor routes and see the real-time position of all participants;
- Use the motorcycle-specific navigator that warns about upcoming dangerous curves;
- Alert the community about issues with your motorcycle using the SOS button;
- Compare fuel prices at nearby gas stations;
- View weather forecasts up to 5 days ahead and along the entire itinerary;
- Set reminders for motorcycle maintenance tasks such as servicing, oil changes, tire replacements, etc.;
- Export a PDF summary of all completed maintenance on your vehicle.

MONETIZATION
Wheelo monetizes through in-app subscriptions, offering plans at €3.49 per month or €29.99 per year to unlock advanced features.

