Bamboo Innovation Studio develops customised technology products, exploiting eXtended Reality. We take the customer's idea beyond the boundaries of the normal screen. We address those who are looking for customised digital solutions, mainly in the cultural sphere, such as museums or exhibitions, and companies that aim to improve customer interaction through virtual environments or to enhance their employees' interactions within business processes by exploiting gamification techniques.

We address
- museums and cultural events: thanks to Mixed Reality, we enrich the experience with immersive and interactive digital elements that would not be possible with any other technology. We combine present and past to create a unique cultural experience;
- companies that want to improve brand engagement: through virtual reality we create immersive showrooms that allow customers to visualise and interact with products wherever they are. The showrooms allow customisation and manipulation of products in real time;
- companies that want to stimulate employees' work: with gamification techniques we make work activities more stimulating, promoting motivation and active participation through playful elements and rewards, improving employee satisfaction and productivity;
- those who want to develop a video game: thanks to the professional training of technical game designers, we are able to design and develop them.

